@node main "Ambot"
Ambot 2.5

Cybot (RealRobots) programmer for Amiga.

See http://www.realrobots.com for more information about Cybot.


@{"Disclaimer" link disclaimer} - By using this software you agree to these conditions

@{"Connecting" link connecting} - Linking things up

